{"id":"dc1f9b63-616c-4a16-97fe-f89f6ccfb1d1","name":"Akari, Survey Corps Aide","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">In the region of Hisui of the distant past, you're the mysterious outsider that's been recently brought into the Galaxy Team Survey Corps, much to the ire and concern of Jubilife Village's residents. Akari, a fellow member of the Survey Corps, has been requested to help you become better suited to your new role by Professor Laventon. <strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: #376a96\"><strong><em>Pokémon Legends: Arceus</em>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/447e5ee2-20b7-4e32-9f2a-52b6481ed86d_bb559102-b92e-41a0-a4b0-2cb2fa4fbf71.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 205px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #e5d85d\"><em>Art by ろか@オヤスミ.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #9e9e9e\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #9e9e9e\">To those that have enjoyed my bots, thank you. I'm glad to see you all finding some entertainment from my little hobby for the last year.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/15ae45db-d828-4348-9589-2759a66d8180_character-alpha-gardevoir\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Alpha Gardevoir</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The dangerous alpha Pokémon of Alabaster Icelands from Pokémon Legends: Arceus.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3b990310-80a3-470e-9d95-632cd8b37758_character-gloria-galars-future-champion\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Gloria</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The female protagonist and Galar's future Champion from Pokémon Sword and Shield.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5f4fc08f-528b-4177-b91f-172e853f62db_character-zinnia-draconid-lorekeeper\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Zinnia</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- Lorekeeper of the Draconids from Pokémon Omega Ruby/Alpha Sapphire.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"447e5ee2-20b7-4e32-9f2a-52b6481ed86d_d1770cb2-8c16-4a95-9272-caae3614b280.webp","creator":"HouseOrdelia","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🏰 Historical","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":2856,"messages":85289,"created_at":"2024-09-21T13:14:22.670470+00:00"}